        dc:description           "Figure L 12. Labels. i Bulimus cercicola Morelet, 1863 ii Bulimus chamaeleon Pfeiffer, 1855 iii Otostomus championi Martens, 1893 iv Bulimus chemnitzioides Forbes, 1850 v Bulimus chimborasensis Reeve, 1848 vi Drymaeus chiriquiensis da Costa, 1901 vii Bulimus cinereus Reeve, 1849." , "Figure 40. Drymaeus species. A-C Drymaeus (Drymaeus) chamaeleon (Pfeiffer, 1855), syntype NHMUK 1975448 (H = 27.6) D-F Drymaeus (Drymaeus) rosenbergi da Costa, 1900, lectotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.17 (H = 19.0) G-I Drymaeus (Drymaeus) zhorquinensis (Angas, 1879), lectotype NHMUK 1879.7.22.15 (H = 46.1) J-L Drymaeus (Drymaeus) ambustus (Reeve, 1849), lectotype NHMUK 1975441 / 1 (H = 29.0). All enlarged." ;
